text.tspan: Number of one-year-olds who have received different vaccinations,
Estimated number of one-year-olds who have received vaccinations for different diseases. This includes tuberculosis ,
diphtheria, pertussis and tetanus (DTP), measles, hepatitis B3, polio , Haemophilus influenzae b (Hib), rubella, and rotavirus .
Data source: WHO/UNICEF; UN, World Population Prospects (2024)
